{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260420060928","title":"Arsitektur bukan kasta; dia harus hidup bersama kode","desc":"Fowler: istilah architecture sering disangka terpisah dari programming, padahal arsitektur yang sehat justru harus mendukung evolusi dan diuji lewat kode.","tags":["permanent-note","software-architecture","architecture","programming"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"367625f74d7ece09f56eae15c2e77681","updated":1776914280156,"created":1776914280156,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.software-architecture","alias":"software-architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.software-architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.architecture","alias":"architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.programming","alias":"programming","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.programming"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.architecture-not-a-blueprint","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":3,"offset":878},"end":{"line":18,"column":53,"offset":928},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.architecture-not-a-blueprint"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":3,"offset":999},"end":{"line":19,"column":52,"offset":1048},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420060847","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":3,"offset":1099},"end":{"line":20,"column":28,"offset":1124},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":3,"offset":2030},"end":{"line":32,"column":28,"offset":2055},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060928"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":3,"offset":1113},"end":{"line":24,"column":28,"offset":1138},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060928"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061259","id":"zettel.20260420061259","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1119},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1144},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060928"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":65,"column":3,"offset":5082},"end":{"line":65,"column":28,"offset":5107},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060928"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"arsitektur-bukan-kasta-dia-harus-hidup-bersama-kode\">Arsitektur bukan kasta; dia harus hidup bersama kode<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#arsitektur-bukan-kasta-dia-harus-hidup-bersama-kode\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fowler curiga terhadap istilah \"architecture\" karena sering memberi kesan bahwa arsitektur terpisah dari programming dan bernuansa elit. Untuknya, arsitektur baik adalah yang mendukung evolusinya sendiri dan terus diuji oleh praktik coding.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Paragraf itu menyerang model pikir \"arsitek bikin blueprint, programmer tinggal eksekusi\".</li>\n<li>Jika arsitektur hanya muncul di slide dan tidak nyambung dengan kode, itu adalah red flag.</li>\n<li>Arsitektur yang sehat harus menjadi kualitas dari keputusan desain yang terus diuji saat sistem berubah.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Peran \"architect\" bukan jabatan, tetapi kemampuan untuk menjaga hubungan antara desain dan implementasi.</li>\n<li>Arsitektur harus berubah bersama kode, bukan tinggal sebagai artefak statis.</li>\n<li>Organisasi yang memisahkan arsitektur dan programming berisiko menghasilkan desain yang tidak bisa dipelihara.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.architecture-not-a-blueprint\">Arsitektur bukan blueprint terpisah dari programming</a> — literatur tentang arsitektur yang tidak terpisah dari programming</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a> — ringkasan halaman Software Architecture Guide</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420060847\">Arsitektur adalah penentu biaya perubahan masa depan</a> — arsitektur sebagai penentu biaya perubahan masa depan</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">programming (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061007\">Halaman Software Architecture Guide adalah peta keputusan, bukan tutorial implementasi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061259\">Arsitektur nyata adalah shared understanding expert developer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"seeds":{"dendron.templates":{}},"enableFullHierarchyNoteTitle":false},"preview":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTags":false,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableKatex":true,"aut